					   <td>

			
			
			


<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%" ID="Table5">
<tr>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="98%">
	
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%" ID="Table6">
		<tr>

		
			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1120">Ak'Anon</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Micro Servos</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Micro Servos</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=44949"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:Olivia_Michael@attglobal.com">Delene of Prexus</a> | 
		                        1/8/2000 4:45:39 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2"><font face="Comic Sans MS, Comic Sans">
Ok, can anyone tell me what to do with these damn <b>Micro Servos</b>?<br>
They are a No Drop item and you can have as many as you can carry at one time (in stacks of 20).<br>
<p>
I get <b>Micro Servos</b> off of <b>Rogue & Runaway Clockworks</b> outside of the <b>Steamfont Mills</b>.<br>
Other people have told me the <b>Micro Servo</b> is for the <b>Trueshot Bow</b>, but something leads me to believe that it has other uses slo.<br>
<p>
The junk dealer in fron of the <b>Necromancer</b> caves says that the <b>Gemchoppers</b> no longer allow him to accept <b>Micro Servos</b> anymore.<br>
If this item is for the <b>Trueshot Bow</b> only, why would the <b>Gemchoppers</b> care?<br>
<p>
I have tried turning the <b>Micro Servos</b> in to the two guys in <b>Gemchopper's Hall</b> in lots of 1,2 3 & 4 to no avail.<br>
I am curently hoarding them in the bank in case of usefulness.<br>
<p>
If anyone can shed a little light on this I would greatly appreciate it!<br>
<p>
Delene (cutest damn female gnome)<br>
11th Season, Cleric of Bristlebane, Prexus<br>
<p>
</font>
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
