			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I've done the trueshot quest many times so am frequently in Steamfont to get servos.  I usually do a shout offering 3 or 4 platinum for looting rights since they are sometimes a pain in the arse to get.  Even if you can kill them in one hit, you still have to go through 20 sometimes before you get a servo.  <BR>
The fletching skill needed to make the Trueshot Bow is at least 150, I tried 29 times before that and failed every time.  Currently I have 202 skill (max I believe) and have yet to fail on it.  This is a time consuming quest but the bows sell easily for 200p, and it eventually pays off the cost of increasing fletching skill and you start to make big profit.<BR>
<BR>

				</font>
